  "keyFeatures": [
    "Automated PostgreSQL failover and self-healing using Kubernetes-native mechanisms",
    "High availability with primary/replica clusters and synchronous replication",
    "Comprehensive backup and recovery via CNPG-I plugins, volume snapshots, and WAL archiving",
    "Declarative management of PostgreSQL roles, databases, extensions, and tablespaces",
    "Connection pooling via native PgBouncer (Pooler CRD) integration",
    "Replica clusters for cross-Kubernetes-cluster disaster recovery and distributed topologies",
    "Prometheus-compatible metrics exporter with customizable queries",
    "kubectl plugin (cnpg) for simplified cluster operations",
    "TLS support with cert-manager integration",
    "Rolling updates with immutable infrastructure model"
  ],
  "publicApiSurface": [
